description: Aren't sure if the dishes in your dishwasher are clean or dirty? Ask Alexa! She'll remember the status of your dishes, so you can ask her next time you open up the dishwasher.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask the dishwasher if the dishes are dirty
Alexa, ask the dishwasher about the dishes
Alexa, tell the dishwasher the dishes are clean
name: The Dishwasher
shortDescription: Ask Alexa about the dishes in your dishwasher.
